WEBVTT

00:10:29.335 --> 00:10:31.696
I think kids should be learning
how to play poker,

00:10:31.720 --> 00:10:35.212
because I think it can teach them
so much about decision making,

00:10:35.236 --> 00:10:37.540
about themselves, about self-control.

00:10:37.926 --> 00:10:40.593
AG: Maria's experience
highlights something about passion

00:10:40.617 --> 00:10:42.006
that most people get wrong.

00:10:42.030 --> 00:10:45.212
Passion is a consequence of effort,
not just a cause.

00:10:46.212 --> 00:10:48.577
Take a recent study of entrepreneurs.

00:10:48.601 --> 00:10:50.871
When they weren't excited
about their start-ups,

00:10:50.895 --> 00:10:52.061
but put time in anyway,

00:10:52.085 --> 00:10:55.283
they actually became
more enthusiastic over the next week.

00:10:55.307 --> 00:10:58.212
Their passion grew as they made progress.

00:10:58.236 --> 00:11:00.122
Angela Duckworth: "Follow your bliss."